text.tspan: Don't let the numbering fool you, it's still a quality release. Sorry for all the
chaps that were waiting for 0.1.0, but we're still kinda far from that release..
We're now going to maintain our almost monthly release schedule so you all
can make lame jokes about "that time of the month".. wink
For those who will want to see the 0.1.0 someday soon, please help us. Once
again our greatest need at the moment is the need for artists. So if you can
draw (I'm counting stick figures as drawing so don't be afraid, we won't bite
you) please contact us. Join the forums and come and greet us on the IRC
Well then, I now have to leave you waiting for the 0.0.11 release.
